<div class="ugc-mod reading-notes">
  <div class="hd">
    <h2>
      读书笔记&nbsp;&nbsp;· · · · · ·&nbsp;
          <span class="pl">(<a href="https://book.douban.com/subject/3931477/annotation">共<span property="v:count">6</span>篇</a>)</span>

    </h2>

      <a class="redbutt rr j a_show_login" href="https://www.douban.com/register?reason=annotate" rel="nofollow"><span>我来写笔记</span></a>
  </div>
  

    <div class="bd">
      <ul class="inline-tabs">
        <li class="on"><a href="#rank" id="by_rank" >按有用程度</a></li>
        <li><a href="#page" id="by_page" >按页码先后</a></li>
        <li><a href="#time" id="by_time" >最新笔记</a></li>
      </ul>
      
  <ul class="comments by_rank" >
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="19701647">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/4562386/"><img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u4562386-19.jpg" alt="墨" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/19701647/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/19701647/" class="">第114页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/4562386/" class=" " title="墨">墨</a>
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="19701647">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">小城的那一头立着几处小小的房子，紧紧挨在一起，仿佛彼此间需要互相扶持。每幢房子都朴实无华、毫不起眼，烟熏火燎又歪歪斜斜，都一直悄然无息地隐没在幽深的小巷。它们仿佛从未见识过欢歌笑语的富贵繁华，仿佛笙歌燕舞的狂欢从未将那些模糊不清、隐而不见的窗子震得嗡嗡作响，而明亮的阳光从未在窗玻璃上映出耀眼的金光。这些房子，像怕见生人得胆怯的孩子，孤独的挤在一处，挤在犹太人狭小的城区里。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-07-16 23:07</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">1人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                小城的那一头立着几处小小的房子，紧紧挨在一起，仿佛彼此间需要互相扶持。每幢房子都朴实无华、毫不起眼，烟熏火燎又歪歪斜斜，都一直悄然无息地隐没在幽深的小巷。它们仿佛从未见识过欢歌笑语的富贵繁华，仿佛笙歌燕舞的狂欢从未将那些模糊不清、隐而不见的窗子震得嗡嗡作响，而明亮的阳光从未在窗玻璃上映出耀眼的金光。这些房子，像怕见生人得胆怯的孩子，孤独的挤在一处，挤在犹太人狭小的城区里。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
</span>
</div>

                  </div>
                <div class="pl col-time">
                  <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/19701647/#comments">回应</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
                  2012-07-16 23:07
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
